img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/02/110354_fca602b59eff58005b51a600fbed0859.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F110354_fca602b59eff58005b51a600fbed0859.jpg&h=bd725c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/02/110354_3faf13ace41496cb740ec8de02be47dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F110354_3faf13ace41496cb740ec8de02be47dd.jpg&h=e05a6844&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但最多幾多rpm?好似又無乜實際作用咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇架得個睇字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多好似都有二千rpm"},{"pid":"ecdf0584ad5ff421cd293ad72c2887c559cf0729","tid":2943,"uid":32167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:16:19.000Z","msg":"Muzo都唔知係唔係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3198e278f9bf9fe16b15e32070f084318cf59f6","tid":2943,"uid":35651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:17:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c5e883129dbd6a418e719d3c2ca97526d3a882c","tid":2943,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>indiegogo買左支結他，delay左半年仲未出貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大神出沒主意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d99a3d6ed800be5c585a2bb7c2769569a827408","tid":2943,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:33:50.000Z","msg":"ks 過<br />\n1. pebble time steel &lt;-- 不需多介紹<br />\n2. everyday backpack &lt;-- 多功能相機背囊，幾滿意<br />\n3. aer gym duffle backpack &lt;-- 做 gym notebook 背囊<br />\n4. skinner shoes &lt;-- 好似物又唔係，鞋又唔係，比你做完運動，跑完步著，似赤足鞋概念。<br />\n以上產品都幾滿意，暫未中意伏"},{"pid":"09edf89ab595d2ad980dc9559add84d11008c112","tid":2943,"uid":6431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>KS買過幾樣嘢<br />\nMuzo -- 聲稱貼舊嘢喺啲平面嘅地方咁可以做到conversation shielding同埋減低環境燥音<br />\nTap -- 好似係韓仔做嘅 一個用trackpad畫gesture解鎖macbook嘅software<br />\nSuperbook -- 用android機做base 做一般文書工作嘅notebook 其實即係有keyboard嘅moon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHalo Black -- 前幾日perk嘅 可以用iphone home button隔離嗰啲位置做back button嘅mon貼 類似android嗰啲back button 佢係將你press嗰吓raise上左上角(iphone好多back button都係左上角)<br />\n<br />\nIndiegogo訂過<br />\nSeiun Pro X -- 等到佛誕嘅DAP<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">其實我係留名嘅</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我訂左seiun pro X 等到final check埋依家都未有消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母 又唔撚溝通 遲完又遲 當我地狗咁撚"},{"pid":"25a98a2abd4fdeee86dd8a34b3228f350c2a649b","tid":2943,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有巴打覆，我又講講自己經驗。<br />\nPledge 過嘅好嘢:<br />\nThe Everyday Sling by Peak Design<br />\n係KS幾出名整相機斜孭袋同配件嘅公司，今次出咗一系列20L/30L背囊、tote bag同斜孭袋。expected delivery 係聖誕前後寄到，點知上兩個星期就到咗。到咗嘅Sling同campaign promo入邊嘅一樣，滿意使用中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nZUS Kevlar Charging Cable<br />\n係Indiegogo pledge 咗4條黑色、尼龍面、L型USB頭差電線，data transfer also works，連shipment 60美金。用Kevlar-reinforced, 所以話係&quot;the last cable you'll ever need&quot; 同有&quot;lifetime warranty&quot; lol <br />\n粗用咗4個幾月，一啲爛嘅跡象都無，感覺幾耐用。<br />\n<br />\n伏嘅<br />\nSmoovie <br />\nOn KS So-called for smartphone&amp; Gopro 嘅輕巧video stabiliser. 簡單一句，唔work = pledge咗垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPUGZ wireless earbuds <br />\n2015年頭on KS pledge時話可以經手機一路充一路用，結果得Android 機可以，iphone用家表示fail. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最躁係delay, delay, 再delay, 一年後先收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。Product 本身design係ok, 但各樣配件、耳膠好cheap、唔舒服，Bluetooth connection 一般又有好明顯嘅底噪，實際battery life ~3 hrs. 基本同2016新出嘅各種新無線耳機無得比...</blockquote><br />\n條ZUS我都買左，但未用"},{"pid":"e5b09f24b5f67e86e711f3c6b70a8b2ecdd8c783","tid":2943,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:16:01.000Z","msg":"買muzo，佢地實delay返100年先ship<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98744c68aa7724be1dcef1aa10cf18bb361d490","tid":2943,"uid":35651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:54:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c383e46daa6c597cabefb3dee6119193449157a7","tid":2943,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:55:52.000Z","msg":"strong post lm"},{"pid":"654d79159c149c7abd52ce93322aa609f824aba3","tid":2943,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:56:35.000Z","msg":"kickstarter 第一次就遇到znaps <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b968c2e17a71db8874713b605b646a2b2a877062","tid":2943,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:24:07.000Z","msg":"Kickstart 過果副design deck 都學到好多野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/002215_9d023c41effa44fdad2c2e27c73d5d4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F002215_9d023c41effa44fdad2c2e27c73d5d4e.jpg&h=c4aefea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTitanium 防水筆連防水筆記簿同筆座 行山幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n